er-performer-and-voice-model-of-vtuber-shino-laila-and-kurari-rose-who-accused-wactor-corporation-releases-latest-statement/">指控 WACTOR 的 VTuber Shinorila Claryrose 前表演者/配音模特发表声明</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“指控 WACTOR 的 VTuber Shinorila Claryrose 前表演者/声优发表声明” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/former-performer-and-voice-model-of-vtuber-shino-laila-and-kurari-rose-who-accused-wactor-corporation-releases-latest-statement/embed/#?secret=ntRqFdLA0m#?secret=MEzqTwxXDx" data-secret="MEzqTwxXDx" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow"><p><a href="https://x.com/Eileennoir" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="艾琳诺⚖">艾琳努瓦</a><a href="https://youtube.com/@Eileennoir" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="艾琳努瓦 Ch.">Ch.／</a>艾琳努瓦<a href="https://x.com/Eileennoir" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="艾琳诺⚖"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2696.png" alt="⚖" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></a> /<a href="https://twitch.tv/eileennoir" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="艾琳努瓦">艾琳诺</a></p><cite>YouTube / X（推特）/ Twitch</cite></blockquote><p> （ <em>P2y.jp管理代表“Mr.2”</em> /Virtual Metaverse/VTuber信息） </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-en wp-block-embed-p-2-y-en"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="ksBrz1CjR0"> <a href="https://en.p2y.jp/vtuber-eileennoir-leaves-algorhythm-project-and-goes-independent/">Eileennoir 离开算法项目并独立</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Eileennoir 离开算法项目并独立” — P2y.EN" src="https://en.p2y.jp/vtuber-eileennoir-leaves-algorhythm-project-and-goes-independent/embed/#?secret=EBv3EKxfr8#?secret=ksBrz1CjR0" data-secret="ksBrz1CjR0" width="6